ociety issues. One of the sponsorship priorities is, however, non-material support: the FNS offers a wide range of projects, events and initiatives for scholarship holders.','1 to 2 years','EUR 900 each month plus a contribution to health insurance','unconditional admission to a doctoral programme or enrolment for a post-graduate course\n\n','30 April and 31 October of each year','https://www.daad.de/deutschland/stipendium/datenbank/en/21148-scholarship-database/?status=&origin=192&subjectGrps=&daad=&q=&page=9&detail=10000145','https://www.freiheit.org/content/promotionsfoerderung','','دانشجویان قبول شده در دوره دکتری در یکی از دانشگاه های آلمان می توانند اقدام کنند.','',1),(367,'2017-03-05 11:08:15','2017-03-05 11:08:15','Friedrich Ebert Foundation: Scholarship for International Students\n\n',4,NULL,'Applicants come from Africa, Asia, Latin America and Eastern Europe. Students in any subject area are eligible to apply, if they demonstrate excellent school or academic merit, wish to study in Germany and are committed to the values of social democracy. Scholarships are awarded to highly-performing students and include a comprehensive seminar programme to help enhance the candidates\\\' social competences and academic skills. Individual support by an on-site liaison lecturer is another benefit of the sponsorship.','maximum funding period corresponds to BAföG regulations\n\n',' monthly base amount of up to EUR 650 + other allowances','admission to study or enrolment at a state or state-recognized higher-education institution in Germany\n\n','http://www.fes.de/studienfoerderung/bewerbung/fristen','https://www.daad.de/deutschland/stipendium/datenbank/en/21148-scholarship-database/?status=&origin=192&subjectGrps=&daad=&q=&page=9&detail=10000153','','','دانشجویان قبول شده در دوره دکتری در یکی از دانشگاه های آلمان می توانند اقدام کنند.','',1),(368,'2017-03-05 11:08:15','2017-03-05 11:08:15','Friedrich Ebert Foundation: Scholarship for International Doctoral Students\n\n',4,