90,'2017-03-05 11:08:19','2017-03-05 11:08:19','Postdoctoral Researchers International Mobility Experience (P.R.I.M.E.)',6,NULL,'Research stay: 12 months outside of Germany and 6 months at a German university. The second link is the application portal.  The university will appoint a mentor/scientific host. The foreign host institution shall be selected according to the scientific preferences/needs of the applicant and the research project. It can be a university, a non-university research institute, or an industrial research entity.  DAAD cannot make funding available to the foreign host institution. ','18 months','Work contract: 3,500‒4,500 €/month + additional allowances','Postdocs.  invitation letter from the German host.  The host institution in Germany has to be a university. The German host university must confirm in writing that the postdoc will be employed for the whole funding period.','deadline for this year has passed!!','https://www.daad.de/deutschland/stipendium/datenbank/en/22962-postdoctoral-researchers-international-mobility-experience/','https://www.daad.de/deutschland/stipendium/datenbank/en/22962-postdoctoral-researchers-international-mobility-experience/','new application cycle announcements in December 2017','بورس برای پسادکتری که 12 ماه در یک کشور غیر از آلمان مشخص و سپس 6 ماه را در خود آلمان می گذرانند. لینک دوم لیست بورس ها را می دهد. متقاضی نیاز به نامه قبولی از دانشگاه آلمانی دارد. کشور خود متقاضی ممکن است نتواند به عنوان کشور خارجی برای انجام تحقیق باشد چون متقاضی باید در 3 سال گذشته به مدت کمتر از 12 ماه در آن کشور زندگی کرده باشد.','List of universities and their PRIME contact person: https://www.daad.de/deutschland/stipendium/datenbank/en/37548-p-r-i-m-e-contact-persons-at-german-universities/ ',1),(391,'2017-03-05 11:08:19','2017-03-05 11:08:19','Bilateral exchange of academics',6,NULL,'Research and study visits as part of bilateral exchange of researchers and scholars with partner countries. To improve international relations and bilateral research cooperations between German and foreign universities, the DAAD supports exchanges of scientists and academics from partner countries. The most important selection criteria are: \nAcademic achievements and, if applicable, publications, which must be documented in the curriculum vitae and a list of publications + A convincing and well-planned research project','2 weeks–3 months','2,000 for assistant teachers, assistant professors and lecturers –2,150 for for professors €/month','Foreign academics and scientists with a doctoral degree that work at a university or research institute in their home country.','01.09.2016 ','https://www.daad.de/deutschland/stipendium/datenbank/en/21148-scholarship-database/?detail=50015508','','Funding may only be claimed once within three years.','فرصت های تحقیقاتی تبادلات دو جانبه برای اساتید و محققان دانشگاه های ایرانی کهروابط بین دانشگاهی در حوزه تحقیقاتی خاص با آلمان دارند. اساتید یا کارکنان دارای مدرک دکتری و مشغول به کار در دانشگاه می توانند برای یک دوره 2 هفته تا 3 ماه برای انجام تحقیقات در یک موسسه آلمانی اقدام کنند تا زمینه برای همکاری مشترک بین دو استاد و دو دانشگاه فراهم شود. ممکن است این بورس فقط برای دانشگاه تهران باشد.  ','',1),(392,'2017-03-05 11:08:20','2017-03-05 11:08:20','Research grants –One-year and short-term grants',3,NULL,'Research or training project at a state-run or state-recognised university or non-university research institute in Germany','7 months to usually 10 months','750‒1,000 €/month + additional allowances','If you are not a citizen of the United States or Canada, you must have obtained last degree in the US/Canada. PhD students; Postdocs / Junior researchers','4th of November, 2016 ','https://www.daad.de/deutschland/stipendium/datenbank/en/21148-scholarship-database/?status=3&origin=32&subjectGrps=F&daad=1&q=&page=2&detail=57140602','https://www.daad.de/deutschland/stipendium/datenbank/en/21148-scholarship-database/?status=3&origin=32&subjectGrps=F&daad=1&q=&page=2&detail=50015434','','این به درد دانشجویان ما نمی خورد چون متقاضی باید آخرین مدرکش را از آمریکا یا کانادا گرفته باشد.','undone - tag',1),(393,'2017-03-05 11:08:20','2017-03-05 11:08:20','Research grants –Doctoral programmes in Germany',6,NULL,'Doctoral project (individual or structured programme) at a state-run or state-recognised university or non-university research institute in Germany OR participation in a structured doctoral study programme. The aim of this grant programme is to support doctoral projects in Germany. Selection Criteria: a convincing and well-planned research project or course of continuing education and academic achievements.','Up to 3 years','750 for graduates‒1,000 for doctoral candidates €/month + additional allowances','PhD students or graduates with a Master\\\'s degree + acceptance letter','42612','https://www.daad.de/deutschland/stipendium/datenbank/en/21148-scholarship-database/?status=4&origin=5&subjectGrps=&daad=&q=&page=2&detail=57135739','','','فارغ التحصیلان دارای مدرک فوق لیسانس می توانند به عنوان دانشجوی دکتری برای یکی از برنامه های دکتری در دانشگاه یا موسسات آلمان اقدام کنند. متقاضی نیاز به نامه قبولی از استاد آلمانی دارد','',1),(394,'2017-03-05 11:08:20','2017-03-05 11:08:20','Research grants –Binationally supervised doctoral degrees',6,NULL,'Doctoral degree at home university with integrated research phases in Germany. DAAD research grants provide foreign doctoral candidates and young academics and scientists with an opportunity to carry out research and continue their education in Germany. The aim of this programme is to promote doctoral degrees at the home university with integrated research phases in Germany. The doctoral degrees are supervised both by a university teacher at the home university and an academic adviser at the host institute in Germany (\\\"sandwich model\\\"). Based on this flexible, multi-phase funding system, doctoral candidates start their doctoral degree in their home country but subsequently spend research periods in Germany. The doctorate is completed in the home country under the supervision of the German academic adviser. ','12 months to 2 years','1,000 €/month + additional allowances during stay(s) in Germany+ Travel and accommodation expenses for supervising university teachers for one trip of up to 10 days.','PhD students. English language proficiency. Proposal must be coordinated with the academic advisers at the home university and in Germany. Applicants should outline how they plan to divide their time between Germany and the home university and specify plans to visit a third country for the purpose of collecting material in a work and time schedule in their application.','42613','https://www.daad.de/deutschland/stipendium/datenbank/en/21148-scholarship-database/?daad=&detail=57135740&origin=104&page=2&q=&status=&subjectGrps=','','During stays at their home university, the grant is interrupted.','دانشجویان دکتری یا قبول شده دکتری می توانند برای این بورس اقدام کنند تا در مدت تحصیلشان بتوانند در یک موسسه یا دانشگاه آلمان تحقیقات مربوط به تز خود را انجام دهند. یک استاد آلمانی در کنار استاد راهنما خودشان باید آنها را راهنمایی کند که روی پروپوزال و تز نیز نظر می دهد. دانشجو باید از اول مدت اقامت خود در آلمان را مشخص کند. مدرک توسط دانشگاه مبدا اهدا می شود. استاد ایرانی یا آلمانی در این بورس می تواند به مدت 10 روز به کشور مقصد جهت نظارت بر کار دانشجو سفر کند.','',1),(395,'2017-03-05 11:08:20','2017-03-05 11:08:20','Re-invitation programme for former scholarship holders',3,NULL,'\nThe aim of this programme is to enable former scholarship holders to carry out research and working projects in Germany and to maintain contacts as part of DAAD\\\'s global alumni network. Research and work projects at a state-run or state-recognised HEI or non-university research institute. ','1‒3 months only','2,000 for assistant teachers, assistant professors and lecturers‒2,150 for for professors €/month + travel allowances','Former holders of DAAD research grants or study scholarships, who were funded for a period of over six months.\nFormer East German scholarship holders who studied for at least one year in Germany, Academic achievements and publications, well-planned research or work project.  Applicants must have returned to their home country at least three years previously. The research or working project must be coordinated with a cooperation partner in Germany.','01.09.2016 ','https://www.daad.de/deutschland/stipendium/datenbank/en/21148-scholarship-database/?daad=&detail=50015492&origin=&page=1&q=wiedereinladung&status=&subjectGrps=','','Will the stay in Germany have a sustainable effect on your professional activity?\nCan you expect it to have multiplier effects, for example, in the form of planned publications?\nWill your stay in Germany promote existing cooperations?','دارندگان مدرک دکتری که قبلا از بورس دااد با مدت مشخص شده در جدول استفاده کرده اند، پس از 3 سال بازگشت به وطنشان می توانند از این بورس با کمک یک استاد آلمانی که قرار است با او پروژه تحقیقاتی یا کاری مشترک انجام دهند، استفاده کنند. حداکثر مدت بورس 3 ماه است و غیرقابل تمدید.','',1),(396,'2017-03-05 11:08:20','2017-03-05 11:08:20','Study Visits by Groups of Foreign Students',4,NULL,'Study trips for groups of a maximum of 15 students accompanied by one university teacher. Individual doctoral candidates may also be funded after consultation with the DAAD. The groups visit at least two German universities where they participate in the academic programme. A cultural programme is to be organised in the evenings and at weekends.','7 to 12 days','50 €/person per day + a mobility lump sum per person','Registered students, at least one completed semester, the university teacher should apply for them','1 Feb, 1 May, 1 Nov.','https://www.daad.de/deutschland/stipendium/datenbank/en/21148-scholarship-database/?detail=10000016','https://www.daad.de/hochschulen/ausschreibungen/projekte/de/11342-foerderprogramme-finden/?s=1&projektid=57144084 ','Individual doctoral candidates may also be funded after consultation with the DAAD.','گروه کمتر از 15 نفر از دانشجویان می توانند از طریق استاد و دانشگاه خود برای یکی از ملاقات های آمده در لینک دوم اقدام کنند تا دااد مبلغ کمک هزینه سفر و اقامت این گروه را پرداخت کند.','',1),(397,'2017-03-05 11:08:20','2017-03-05 11:08:20','DLR-DAAD Research Fellowships',5,NULL,'DLR-DAAD Fellowships offer outstanding scientists and researchers the opportunity to conduct special research at the institutes of the DLR in Germany. The application procedure occurs online through the DAAD online portal. Furthermore, your referees should send the hardcopies of the letters of recommendation to the application address by post.','PhD students: 36 months, PostDoc: 6‒24 months, Prof.: 1‒3 months','1,500–2,300 €/month + additional allowances','You can apply only for a DLR institute, TOEFL: 550/217','','www.daad.de/dlr','https://www.daad.de/deutschland/stipendium/datenbank/de/15371-dlr-daad-research-fellowships-current-offers/ ','','اساتید یا پسادکتری یا دانشجوی دکتری در زمینه های گفته شده می توانند برای مدت گفته شده برای تحقیقات در یکی از موسسات DLR آلمان اقدام کنند. وبسایت دوم لیستی از پروژه های موجود در هر زمان را می دهد.','',1),(398,'2017-03-05 11:08:21','2017-03-05 11:08:21','NoDescription',1,NULL,'','','','','','','','','ناقص','undone - tag ERROR-NO Description',1),(399,'2017-03-05 11:09:43','2017-03-05 11:09:43','Funding in each institute',6,NULL,'Fraunhofer EU Office Brussels; Fraunhofer Austria Research in Vienna and Graz; Fraunhofer Italia Research in Bolzano; Fraunhofer Portugal Research in Porto; Fraunhofer UK Research Ltd. in Glasgow; Stiftelsen Fraunhofer Chalmers Centrum för Industimatematik in Gothenburg Germany; Fraunhofer USA Michigan; Fraunhofer in Canada; Fraunhofer in Brazil; Fraunhofer in Chile; Fraunhofer in Asia: CHINA; INDIA; INDONESIA; JAPAN; KOREA; MALAYSIA; SINGAPORE; Fraunhofer in Africa and the Gulf States:  United Arab Emirates; Egypt; South Africa\n\n ','Depends on the program','Depends on the program','Depends on the program','Depends on the program','http://www.standortkarte.fraunhofer.de/main.jsp?lang=en&debug=false&topic=institut&topicvalue=null&focus=world&focusvalue=','','','هر شعبه فارنهوفر به طور مجزا  خودش یک سری بورس ارائه می دهد. لیستی از این شعب ارائه شده در ضمن لینک اول نقشه ای از همه این شعب با جزییات و آدرس وبسایت آنها را دارد. ','undone - tag',5),(400,'2017-03-05 11:09:43','2017-03-05 11:09:43','Cooperation with the Max Planck Society',1,NULL,'This collaboration aims to bridge the gap between basic and applied research by improving cooperation between the institutes of the Fraunhofer-Gesellschaft and those of the Max Planck Society. Since the initiative was launched, a whole series of research projects have been evaluated and approved by internal and independent experts. List of projects that will go on till 2017: HEUSLER - New magnetic materials without rare earth elements\n','','','','','https://www.mpg.de/cooperation-with-fraunhofer','','','این هزینه برای مشارکت فارنهوفر و ماکس پلانک است. پروژه های تحقیقاتی آن همه تعریف شده اند و اکثرا یا تمام شده اند یا تا آخر 2016 تمام می شوند. فقط یک پروژه را نوشته که تا آخر 2017 ادامه دارد. ','undone - tag ERROR-NO Rating',5),(401,'2017-03-05 11:09:43','2017-03-05 11:09:43','Internships for Students',4,NULL,'At Fraunhofer, students in all kinds of disciplines find the ideal environment in which to get to grips with topics connected to our research topics. As an intern at one of our institutes, you’ll work on active projects and gain fascinating insights into practical research while you’re studying.','Depends on the program','Depends on the program','Depends on the program','Depends on the program','https://recruiting.fraunhofer.de/Jobs/2?Reset=G&lang=eng&searchFunction=10080&search1','https://www.fraunhofer.de/en/jobs-and-career/students.html','','لیستی از کارآموزی های موجود در موسسات فارنهوفر در لینک اول آمده است. اینکه کمک مالی ارائه می شود یا نه مشخص نیست.','',5),(402,'2017-03-05 11:09:43','2017-03-05 11:09:43','Fraunhofer Attract',6,NULL,'International specialists in application-oriented research can set up a new research group at a Fraunhofer Institute to develop their ideas towards actual innovations. They receive substantial funding, both budgetary and recruiting responsibility and conduct research in close cooperation with industry at state-of-the-art Fraunhofer laboratories. The application must be submitted jointly by the researcher and the Fraunhofer Institute into which the research group is to be integrated.','5 years (3+2)','Max. 2.5 million euros',' researchers may not be in the employ of the Fraunhofer-Gesellschaft at the time of application, need existing contacts to their desired Fraunhofer Institute. The application must be submitted jointly by the researcher and the Fraunhofer Institute into which the research group is to be integrated.','Filing the application: March 28, 2017; October 10, 2017','https://www.fraunhofer.de/en/jobs-and-career/seasoned-professionals/fraunhofer-attract.html','https://www.fraunhofer.de/content/dam/zv/en/Jobs%20and%20Career/Attract/Grant-Information-Fraunhofer-Attract.pdf','','گرنت بسیار زیاد به مدت 5 سال که به استادی داده می شود که پروژه بسیار خاصی ارائه کند. این استاد باید از قبل با یکی از موسسات فارنهوفر ارتباط داشته باشد و پروژه را در یکی از موسسات فارنهوفر تعریف کند.. اینکه استاد باید از آلمان اقدام کند یا جای دیگر هم می تواند مشخص نیست. ','',5),(403,'2017-03-05 11:09:43','2017-03-05 11:09:43','Jobs at Fraunhofer',4,NULL,'Jobs for students or scientists + postdoc positions+ student assistant jobs+ projects for students at different levels + Thesis research positions at different levels','Depends on the program','Depends on the program','Depends on the program','Depends on the program','https://recruiting.fraunhofer.de/Jobs/2','https://www.fraunhofer.de/en/jobs-and-career.html','','لینک دوم یکی دیتابیس کامل از همه شغل ها یا فعالیت هایی است که برای دانشجویان یا اساتید موجود است. ',' ERROR-NO Tag',5),(404,'2017-03-05 11:09:43','2017-03-05 11:09:43','Fraunhofer Academy',4,NULL,'The Fraunhofer Academy is the Fraunhofer-Gesellschaft’s specialist provider of continuing education and part-time training for people in employment. The Fraunhofer Academy offers specialists and managers outstanding courses of study, certificate courses and seminars based on the research activities of the Fraunhofer institutes in collaboration with selected and prestigious partner universities.','Depends on the program','Depends on the program','Depends on the program','Depends on the program','https://www.fraunhofer.de/en/research/range-of-services/further-training.html','http://www.academy.fraunhofer.de/en.html','','موسسه تحصیلات دانشگاهی که کلاس های آموزشی نیز برگزار می کند. بورسی اینجا داده نمی شود.','',5),(405,'2017-03-05 11:09:43','2017-03-05 11:09:43','Spin Offs',3,NULL,'Fraunhofer Venture: internal Fund with 1.5 Mio. Euro p.a. to support\nspin-off-projects; > 50% of spin-offs are financed by VCs,\nBusiness Angels and banks; Fraunhofer Venture. The services that Fraunhofer Venture provides are: Prequalification program\n1) Business Ideation: Faunhofer employees develop business ideas and test them for effective customer use. 2) Business model development: FDays\nFraunhofer Days: Recycling Open acceleration mode selected, entrepreneurially minded employees. 3) Business planning: FFE: \nFraunhofer promotes entrepreneurs: Internal promotion, in support of the preparatory activities for the establishment of a Fraunhofer spin-offs. 4) Management support: FFM: Fraunhofer Fosters Management: Financial support from Fraunhofer investments to complete important management skills.\n','','','part of the research team in one of their institutes ','','http://www.fraunhoferventure.de/','','','فارنهوفر برای کسانیکه در یکی از موسساتش تصمیم به بناگزاری یک استارت آپ را بکنند از طریق واحد Fraunhofer Venture خود برایشان حمایت معنوی ایجاد می کند. این ایده باید در خود آلمان نیز به اجرا در بیاید. کمک مالی به کارآفرین نیز از طریق حمایت های خصوصی است که خودش یا فارنهوفر برایش پیدا کنند.','undone - tag',5),(406,'2017-03-05 11:09:44','2017-03-05 11:09:44','PhD position',6,NULL,'Alternatively, the Fraunhofer institute might be able to offer a PhD position. Vacancies can be found through the online career platform: http://www.fraunhofer.de/en/jobs-and-career.html.  List of Fraunhofer institutes: https://www.fraunhofer.de/en/institutes/institutes-and-research-establishments-in-germany.html','3 years with possible extension up to 6 years','Depends on the program','Depends on the program','Depends on the program','https://recruiting.fraunhofer.de/Jobs/2?Reset=G&lang=eng&searchFunction=10040&search1','','','دانشجویان علاقمند به اقدام برای گذراندن دوره دکتری در یکی از موسسات فارنهوفر هستند می توانند فرصت های موجود را از لینک داده شده پیدا کنند.  کمک مالی بسته به برنامه و موسسه آن دارد. ','',5),(407,'2017-03-05 11:09:44','2017-03-05 11:09:44','PhD Student Stay',3,NULL,'In some cases Fraunhofer might decide to establish an exchange program with an international partner which is tailored to meet the demands of both partners. Such a program may take the following form:\n \nExcellent Ph.D. students are offered the chance to experience practical research in relation to their doctoral thesis at a German Fraunhofer Institute.\nThe period of doctoral training and research at Fraunhofer is one year.\nThe academic title is awarded by the home organization, not by Fraunhofer.\nDuring their research stay, the PhD students receive a scholarship which is paid by the home organization.\nThe candidates are selected by the home organization.\nThe candidates are given guidance from Fraunhofer Headquarters to find appropriate Fraunhofer institutes.\nCandidates apply at up to three possible host Fraunhofer-Institutes in regards to the topic of their doctoral thesis.\nThe decision about an acceptance is made by Fraunhofer and the particular Fraunhofer institute.\n\nFraunhofer will support students in the following ways:\nCultural and administrative preparation before the students come to Germany.\nOrganization of a get-together of all students at Fraunhofer HQ in Munich some months after their start in Germany: Cross- Cultural Training, Exchange of Experience, Sightseeing.\nAs especially knowledge of the English as well as to some extend of the German language is crucial, language courses in advance and during the stay could be organized.','1 year','','phD Students+ Exchange contract','','http://ic.aut.ac.ir/en/?page_id=1774','','','برای دانشجویان دکتری امیرکبیر که بتوانند برای مدت 1 سال برای تحقیقات در فارنهوفر بمانند، دانشگاه باید با این موسسه قرارداد همکاری امضا نماید. البته دانشگاه باید هزینه دانشجو در آنجا را تقبل کند.','',5),(408,'2017-03-05 11:10:01','2017-03-05 11:10:01','Sofja Kovalevskaja Award\n\n',3,NULL,'Submit an application if you are a successful top-rank junior researcher from abroad, only completed your doctorate with distinction in the last six years, and have published work in prestigious international journals or publishing houses. The Sofja Kovalevskaja Award allows you to spend five years building up a working group and working on a high-profile, innovative research project of your own choice at a research institution of your own choice in Germany.\nScientists and scholars from all disciplines may apply online to the Alexander von Humboldt Foundation . The Humboldt Foundation plans to grant up to six Sofja Kovalevskaja Awards. The award is valued at up to €1.65 million.','Award allows you to spend five years building up a working group ','up to six Sofja Kovalevskaja Awards. The award is valued at up to €1.65 million. Eachone about € 275.000','Doctorate or comparable academic degree (Ph.D., C.Sc. or equivalent), completed with distinction less than six years prior to the application submission deadline. Should it not be possible or customary to take a Ph.D. in your subject or country of origin, you may apply up to ten years after completing your Master\\\'s or Diploma Degree provided that your publication record is commensurate with a Ph.D. and your current career stage.\nCareer level: the award would enable the successful applicant to take on a leadership position (e.g. head of a junior research group) in Germany for the first time. Moreover, the applicant must not have held or accepted an offer of permanent employment in Germany. The relevant date is the date of the selection.\nCutting-edge academic achievements documented particularly by a comprehensive list of independent academic publications reviewed according to international standards and printed in journals and/or by publishing houses.\nSupport of the German host institution, evidenced by a detailed expert\\\'s report from the academic host as well as the host\\\'s agreement and the confirmation from the administration at the host institution.\nTwo supporting expert reviews from academics (at the applicant\\\'s own institute or other institutes, where possible including some outside the applicant\\\'s country of origin).\nLanguage skills: scholars in the humanities or social sciences and physicians must have a good knowledge of German if it is necessary to carry out the project successfully; otherwise a good knowledge of English; scientists and engineers must have a good knowledge of German or English.\nNo previous Sofja Kovalevskaja Award.\nOrigin: Foreign academics staying in Germany are eligible to apply if they have lived outside Germany for a minimum of 12 months in total in the 18-month period prior to the application submission deadline. Educational residents are subject to the regulations governing Germans. German academics are eligible to apply if they have been working in an academic capacity abroad for a longer time. For more details please check with the FAQ.\nThe Humboldt Foundation assumes that candidates will abide by the Rules of Good Scientific Practice and the legally-binding principles of scientific ethics during the application and sponsorship periods.','next application round is scheduled to start in Spring 2017','https://www.humboldt-foundation.de/web/kovalevskaja-award.html','','','برنامه ای جهت افرادی که حداکثر سال است دکتری گرفته اند. باید در سطح پژوهشگر حرفه با با قابلیت شبکه سازی و راهبری تیم باشند. این حمایت سالانه برای طرح به مجموع 1.65 میلیون یورو (هر نفر نهایتا 275 هزار یورو) در مدت 5 سال. (اشاره نشده که هر سال این میزان پرداخت میشود یا نهایت این میزان و طرح نهایتا تا 5 سال؟). حتما استاد باید سرآمد باشد و انتشارات بین المللی زیادی داشته باشد.  ','',6),(409,'2017-03-05 11:10:02','2017-03-05 11:10:02','Feodor Lynen Research Fellowship\n\n',6,NULL,'Sponsorship for research stays worldwide by researchers from Germany of all disciplines and at all career stages. Applicants choose an academic host from some 15,000 academics in the Humboldt Network abroad.\n','for post-doctoral researchers (up to four years after completing a doctorate):\n6 to 24 months\nFor experienced researchers (up to 12 years after completing a doctorate):\n6 to 18 months, divisible into a maximum of three visits over three years','The fellowship amount varies according to target country and personal circumstances: a fellow heading for the USA, for example, currently receives €3,305 per month, or up to €5,320 if accompanied by a marital partner and two children. Travel expenses are paid in addition. Moreover, it is possible to apply for a return fellowship to Germany lasting up to 12 months.\nyou can use the followship calcutalor ( https://www.humboldt-foundation.de/web/pub_stipcalc.main ) to calculate the amount you will be funded ','above average academic history and academic record\nhost\\\'s confirmation of research facilities\nExperienced researchers also require:\ntheir own academic profile\nprofessional experience at least at the level of assistant professor or junior research group leader or several years‘ independent scientific employment','At any time','https://www.humboldt-foundation.de/web/lynen-fellowship.html','','','فرصت مطالعات و پژ